OL,7,FSouthampton Container Terminals
OL,8,FLimited has been fined #1million after
OL,9,Fan employee fell 11 metres.
OL,11,F31-year-old Christopher Hooper from
OL,12,FWinchester, suffered fractures to his
OL,13,Fskull, back, pelvis, arm, wrist and
OL,14,Fankle.
OL,16,FHe fell through a open hole in the
OL,17,Fdriver's cab of a straddle carrier,
OL,18,Flanding onto concrete in 2022.
