OL,7,FThe hole had been created by
OL,8,Fcontractors that were replacing a
OL,9,Fglass floor.
OL,11,FThe employee, who had worked for
OL,12,FSouthampton Container Terminals
OL,13,FLimited since he was 17, had been
OL,14,Fundertaking routine maintenance work
OL,15,Fand was unaware of the open hole,
OL,16,Fbefore falling onto the floor.
