OL,7,FHooper, who was 29 at the time of the
OL,8,Fincident, says: "I feel like a puppet
OL,9,Fin my life who is being moved from
OL,10,Ftherapy to therapy with no control
OL,11,Fover where I am going.
OL,13,F"It feels like my life is in a waiting
OL,14,Froom, early out of hospital I had
OL,15,Fcloser milestones that felt achievable
OL,16,Fwhereas now no one can tell me what I
OL,17,Fcan do next and that is really
OL,18,Fimpacting my day-to-day life as I
OL,19,Fdon't know what the rest of my life
OL,20,Fwill look like."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
