OL,4,Cemployee fell 11 metres landing onto
OL,5,Cconcrete
OL,7,FSouthampton Container Terminals
OL,8,FLimited, of Palace Street,
OL,9,FWestminster, London pleaded guilty to
OL,10,Fbreaching Section 2(1) of the Health
OL,11,Fand Safety at Work etc. Act 1974.
OL,13,FThe Company was fined #1 million and
OL,14,Fordered to pay #11,664.59 in costs on
OL,15,F2 August 2024.
OL,17,FHSE inspector Francesca Arnold says:
OL,18,F"This incident has resulted in severe
OL,19,Flife-changing injuries for Mr Hooper,
OL,20,Fwho is lucky to be alive.
