OL,4,Cemployee fell 11 metres landing onto
OL,5,Cconcrete
OL,7,F"His life has completely changed
OL,8,Fbecause of Southampton Container
OL,9,FTerminals Limited's failure to produce
OL,10,Fa suitable risk assessment and
OL,11,Fimplement straightforward control
OL,12,Fmeasures.
OL,14,F"The hazards of working at height are
OL,15,Fwell known and documented and this
OL,16,Fprosecution should now remind
OL,17,Femployers that a failure to manage and
OL,18,Fimplement effective measures can have
OL,19,Fserious consequences and they will be
OL,20,Fheld accountable for this failure."
